# 07 - e-commerce within hzd

## Description
As a user I want to use the e-com options integrated in hzd to send a product to a person from whom I do not know the delivery details

## Acceptance criteria

### 1 - As buyer using hzd I want to specify the user-locator

**Given** I'm in the delivery details selection of the e-commerce platform  
**And given** I have selected the hoozad widget  
**When** I set the recipient user-locator  
**Then** I can submit the widget  

